# Retail Loan & Mortgage Approval

This collection focuses on **Automating mortgage and loan underwriting while managing prepayment and default risks.**.

## Notebooks

- 01_mortgage_default_risk_prediction.ipynb
- 02_automated_underwriting_decision_tree.ipynb
- 03_prepayment_risk_regression.ipynb
- 04_home_appraisal_value_estimation.ipynb
- 05_sme_loan_approval_scoring.ipynb
- 06_debt_to_income_ratio_impact_analysis.ipynb
